│ `VPlan::getVPInstruction`, where `VPInstruction`s are created and initialized.  │
│ We need to add logic to check if all operands are uniform and, if so, set the   │
│ `GeneratesPerFirstLaneOnly` flag.\n\n```cpp\n// In VPlan.cpp, inside            │
