│ 1704 /// A pure virtual base class for all recipes modeling header phis,        │
│ including                                                                       │
│ 1705 /// phis for first order recurrences, pointer inductions and reductions.   │
│ The                                                                             │
│ 1706 /// start value is the first operand of the recipe and the incoming value  │
│ from                                                                            │
│ 1707 /// the backedge is the second operand.                                    │
│ 1708 ///                                                                        │
│ 1709 /// Inductions are modeled using the following sub-classes:                │
│ 1710 ///  * VPCanonicalIVPHIRecipe: Canonical scalar induction of the vector    │
│ loop,                                                                           │
│ 1711 ///    starting at a specified value (zero for the main vector loop, the   │
│ resume                                                                          │
